OL,3,CParents M40 minibus crash victim call
OL,4,Cfor stricter teacher driving rules
OL,6,FTamworth MP Sarah Edwards, has joined
OL,7,Fwith parents campaigning for a
OL,8,Fnational safety standard to be applied
OL,9,Fto all schools.
OL,11,FMs Edwards said it should be mandatory
OL,12,Ffor teachers to hold a D1 licence to
OL,13,Fdrive a minibus.
OL,15,FMrs Fitzgerald said she would prefer
OL,16,Fit if "teachers didn't drive at all,
OL,17,Ffrankly".
OL,19,F"Teachers, teach. Drivers, drive."
OL,26,@xD@GOUyD@HO]{D@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
