PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774253647
OL,3,CParents M40 minibus crash victim call
OL,4,Cfor stricter teacher driving rules
OL,6,FTeachers' union the NASUWT strongly
OL,7,Fadvises members not to drive
OL,8,Fminibuses, and argues it should not be
OL,9,Fpart of their contractual duty.
OL,11,FOne in four teachers have been
OL,12,Fpressured into driving a minibus, a
OL,13,Fsurvey by the union found.
OL,15,FIt also reported one in 10 teachers
OL,16,Fhave been required to drive more than
OL,17,F50 miles after a full day of teaching.
OL,19,FMs Edwards said teachers who are "too
OL,20,Ftired, or aren't confident" should not
OL,21,Fbe behind the wheel.
OL,26,@{D@bOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
