OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774253647
OL,3,CParents M40 minibus crash victim call
OL,4,Cfor stricter teacher driving rules
OL,6,FShe added: "We know that every time we
OL,7,Fget into a car or a vehicle, that you
OL,8,Fcould be in an accident, and it only
OL,9,Ftakes one silly driver or one real
OL,10,Flapse of judgment for that to happen."
OL,12,FIt's as a couple whose daughter was
OL,13,Fkilled in a minibus crash have raised
OL,14,Fconcerns their grandchildren face the
OL,15,Fsame dangers more than 30 years on.
OL,17,FLiz and Steve Fitzgerald's daughter
OL,18,FClaire died in 1993 when the school
OL,19,Fminibus she was in collided with a
OL,20,Florry on the M40.
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
