OL,3,CParents M40 minibus crash victim call
OL,4,Cfor stricter teacher driving rules
OL,6,FCurrent regulations permit any teacher
OL,7,Fwho is over 21 and has held their
OL,8,Fstandard licence for more than two
OL,9,Fyears to drive a minibus which holds
OL,10,Fup to 16 passengers.
OL,12,FUnder section 19 permits, teachers are
OL,13,Fnot required to hold a D1 licence,
OL,14,Fwhich would involve a medical
OL,15,Fexamination, passing a Passenger
OL,16,FCarrying Vehicle (PCV) theory test,
OL,17,Fand passing a practical driving test
OL,18,Fin a 17-seat minibus.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1774253647
OL,3,CParents M40 minibus crash victim call
OL,4,Cfor stricter teacher driving rules
OL,6,FHowever, someone driving for
OL,7,Fcommercial purposes would require a D1
OL,8,Flicence.
OL,10,FThis discrepancy has been criticised
OL,11,Fby Mr Fitzgerald, who questioned why
OL,12,Fschools are not held to higher
OL,13,Fstandards.
OL,15,FHe said he welcomes the progress made
OL,16,Fon road safety over the past 30 years,
OL,17,Fbut said "they don't prevent
OL,18,Faccidents".
OL,26,@yD@JOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
