OL,3,CParents M40 minibus crash victim call
OL,4,Cfor stricter teacher driving rules
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "Road
OL,7,Fsafety is a top priority, and we
OL,8,Fprovide guidance to schools and local
OL,9,Fauthorities on driving minibuses.
OL,10,FDrivers should make sure they have the
OL,11,Fright entitlements, ensure they are
OL,12,Fproperly trained and take regular
OL,13,Fbreaks.
OL,15,F"Ministers from the Department for
OL,16,FTransport and the Department for
OL,17,FEducation have met with campaigners to
OL,18,Flisten to their concerns and will
OL,19,Falways work to make sure staff and
OL,20,Fchildren are safe when travelling to
OL,21,For from school activities."
OL,26,@nD@aOUwD@AOU}D@[O]
